e><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>70000羊 大阪京都5日4夜唔知有冇閒錢shopping..... （機票住宿信用卡比咗）<br />\n想買1/2件衫同鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買野就一定唔夠</blockquote><br />\n我地唔會豪食，可能一日一餐會洗多啲<br />\n同埋想問大阪去邊度買野抵啲，係咪多數去特賣場買</blockquote><br />\n你要買咩？</blockquote><br />\n想睇下有冇短T買幾件或者買對鞋，個筆直都買唔到幾多野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買野呢d野你又唔講買咩 tee係街邊心口寫I love japan，定你買件givenchy? 鞋你買puma定你買Nike mag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直接d講 日牌同香港比有7折左右 歐洲貨日本貴過香港。</blockquote><br />\n鞋諗住Vanz new banlance 嗰啲普通牌子咋，就係貪日牌買平過香港想睇下執唔執到平野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衫又冇話要咩牌子，可能真係買I LOVE JP都得，啱心水就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebaaed03182d838c45b288d8ef019b4ec00dd71","tid":265440,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠哂啦，去東京20000yen洗7日都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排 15000 yen 洗七日。"},{"pid":"09ebef04e5827710ae96af31851f59ed97737f10","tid":265440,"uid":114574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"上星期去完大阪同京都，7日洗左60000幾Yen，有食燒肉放題同蟹道樂，買左藥妝同衫，日本交通費比較貴"},{"pid":"425504032a28881e93cab3d97a7552ddeaacd748","tid":265440,"uid":5728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係大阪玩7日<br />\n大概帶幾多錢到？<br />\n8000洗費夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會點買野 主要用係食方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋大阪一餐大概幾多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8000蚊一個人都夠嘅<br />\n唔買名牌  唔買電子野<br />\n大阪餐廳食一餐唔貴 你預$1000羊至8000羊<br />\n拉麵$1000(碗)<br />\n大阪燒$800(個)<br />\n魚生飯$4000(碗)<br />\n鰻魚飯$4000(set)<br />\n啤酒$400(杯)<br />\n想食下蟹道樂(中午3000羊以上)晚餐貴d<br />\n個價錢學生可能會覺得貴<br />\n但其實對比香港係好抵食而且有質素<br />\n喺香港食d魚生飯都三舊水食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以試︰<br />\n<del>蟹道樂</del><br />\n黑門市場︰可以買生果  <del>一板海膽</del><br />\n<del>亀王らーめん <br />\n北極星 <br />\n自由軒<br />\n法善寺橫丁︰入面有間xx然大阪燒<br />\n本家</del>章魚燒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你旅遊書copy出黎？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3bfdf52959fad9aefd0dd9975f3e395b3ece3ec0","tid":265440,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係大阪玩7日<br />\n大概帶幾多錢到？<br />\n8000洗費夠唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會點買野 主要用係食方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋大阪一餐大概幾多錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三十蚊餐同三千蚊一餐都有"},{"pid":"78a682719e7ffcd3d5191c2839f8b32ed8359f32","tid":265440,"uid":77201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>除非想入USJ, 否則大阪真係冇乜特別洗費, 同埋我覺得大阪最盡都只可以玩到4日<br />\n磯丸水產都係&lt;1500円碗海鮮飯，磯燒既話就3280左右<br />\n章魚燒同大阪燒 800円<br />\n黑門食生&amp;燒蠔、海膽、三文魚子之類都只會用到4000円<br />\n交通有pass買，星期六日好似仲有500円市營地鐵放題</blockquote><br />\n黑門而家 一個海膽最撚細 得你篤精咁小 都賣1000<br />\n蠔一隻都1000。 4000一人份都未必得 只夠sip牙那</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xgquk0lf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxgquk0lf&h=4f10cb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4月去果次影低左<br />\n生蠔同海膽係自己夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完兩轉之後已經冇曬靚蠔 <br />\n好似係洗左2400円 (4份蠔+1個海膽+2次開殼費)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/slivtdjh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fslivtdjh&h=64507466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一間燒蠔賣500円，有3～4粒蠔肉 <br />\n正到行到街尾都要走返回頭再食多次"},{"pid":"ad0afd89a97eed02868323d97e8ed9c11bba821c","tid":265440,"uid":77201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>除非想入USJ, 否則大阪真係冇乜特別洗費, 同埋我覺得大阪最盡都只可以玩到4日<br />\n磯丸水產都係&lt;1500円碗海鮮飯，磯燒既話就3280左右<br />\n章魚燒同大阪燒 800円<br />\n黑門食生&amp;燒蠔、海膽、三文魚子之類都只會用到4000円<br />\n交通有pass買，星期六日好似仲有500円市營地鐵放題</blockquote><br />\n黑門而家 一個海膽最撚細 得你篤精咁小 都賣1000<br />\n蠔一隻都1000。 4000一人份都未必得 只夠sip牙那</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xgquk0lf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxgquk0lf&h=4f10cb0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4月去果次影低左<br />\n生蠔同海膽係自己夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完兩轉之後已經冇曬靚蠔 <br />\n好似係洗左<span style=\"color: red;\">4300</span>円 (4份蠔+1個海膽+2次開殼費)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/slivtdjh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fslivtdjh&h=64507466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一間燒蠔賣500円，有3～4粒蠔肉 <br />\n正到行到街尾都要走返回頭再食多次</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbcc35b7d639d7cd2eb1e0b744ba3ac3cff08669","tid":265440,"uid":37672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:50:03.000Z","msg":"咁細隻蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手掌咁大都係1000 北海道產"},{"pid":"1e665fd24de586f4b5bac7cb7e8e8a1a07e74be5","tid":265440,"uid":77201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁細隻蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手掌咁大都係1000 北海道產</blockquote><br />\n蠔唔是睇大細 係睇蠔殼深唔深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深先係代表隻蠔夠鮮甜同濃味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcda6edd5756b44fd8374371c343457d7bda61d5","tid":265440,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁細隻蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手掌咁大都係1000 北海道產</blockquote><br />\n<br 