yTime":"2017-06-01T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"夠喇，我換咗HKD6000<br />\n玩5日，主要都係食野多<br />\n買咗兩對跑鞋同好多零食"},{"pid":"7b54a9d35a386cb2a90653e5a171cc478e5527fb","tid":265440,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夠喇，我換咗HKD6000<br />\n玩5日，主要都係食野多<br />\n買咗兩對跑鞋同好多零食</blockquote><br />\n交通同shopping洗咗幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想參考下"},{"pid":"53f8419cdfcc4dd268c19e3d155f0da490b2ff5a","tid":265440,"uid":5239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T13:45:48.000Z","msg":"玩9日<br />\n洗左8000<br />\n交通 1000多D<br />\n入景點+Postcard 1000左右<br />\n買野 1500<br />\n其他都係食"},{"pid":"d0a4534525cfd8c96fc8f3d1d4632c706ffe15be","tid":265440,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:42:48.000Z","msg":"前幾年又係考完dse <br />\n我估你都係？<br />\n去六日五夜 當地使費五千蚊到"},{"pid":"05a824facdbb090434283905fc353a1bbadb87c5","tid":265440,"uid":46635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪點玩到七日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去埋神户姬路京都奈良啦<br />\n啱啱喺神户返大阪<br />\n第三日唔計買嘢用咗30000yen左右</blockquote><br />\n我會啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係諗緊點分配日子<br />\n3日大阪應該夠？"}]}